# Frontend

- Functional components + TypeScript; routing in `frontend/src/App.tsx` (react-router-dom).
- HTTP calls via `frontend/src/api/` (`client.ts`, `transactionsApi.ts`, `portfolioApi.ts`, `portfoliosApi.ts`, `statsApi.ts`, `budgetsApi.ts`, `authApi.ts`).
- Display currency: context in `frontend/src/state/currency.tsx`.
- Formatting: `frontend/src/utils/format.ts`.
- Styles: existing classes in `App.css` / `index.css` — match the current UI layout.
- Routes and API mapping: [docs/frontend.md](mdc:docs/frontend.md) — add a row when adding pages or client functions.
